technically you are correct, however in the spirit of the rathe this is an inconsistancy.<br>
<br>
For instance, if 2 guilds band together to kill the AoW (because for one reason or another they could not do it alone) all other independent rotations become merged as an alliance.<br>
<br>
I.e.: if guild X kills kt,dain,yeli,tov,ct by them selves, and Guild Y does the same, if they were to do a Guild X&amp;Y kill of AoW, then separate rotations of guild x and guild y would become merged.<br>
<br>
